Author: Aygurlitsyaalt
Text: Sadly, not many of us know how to fix the mental aspect, the voice or especially the obsessive thinking. Which is why we are here lol. But the benefit is knowing we aren't alone and we have a non-judgmental place to vent.   You definitely are not alone and you 100% deserve to eat whatever amount you need to walk with your dog and and go thru your day! ðŸ’–
